UPDSLEEPMODE for MacOSX (ssd hack)
author: Ivan Koshkin <ivan@koshkin.me>

installation:

sudo -s
cp com.morgoth.... /Library/LaunchDaemons
chown root /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.morgoth....
launchctl load /Library/LaunchDaemons/com.morgoth...

copy updsleepmode.sh to some directory
modify updsleepmode's path in plist

